{"id": "art-1551", "label": "Art. 1551", "title": "Art. 1551", "slug": "art-1551", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2047450912\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2025\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2047450912\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 155<sup>1</sup></span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1751418419\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2024\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1751418419\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Dac&#259; adunarea general&#259; nu introduce <span\nclass=SpellE>ac&#355;iunea</span> în r&#259;spundere prev&#259;zut&#259; la\nart. </span><span style='color:#1B1B1B'>155</span><span style='color:black'> <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> nici nu d&#259; curs propunerii unuia sau mai\nmultor <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionari</span> de a <span class=SpellE>ini&#355;ia</span>\no asemenea <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iune</span>, <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionarii</span>\nreprezentând, individual sau împreun&#259;, cel <span class=SpellE>pu&#355;in</span>\n5% din capitalul social au dreptul de a introduce o <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iune</span>\nîn desp&#259;gubiri, în nume propriu, dar în contul <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>,\nîmpotriva oric&#259;rei persoane prev&#259;zute la art. </span><span\nstyle='color:#1B1B1B'>155 alin. (1)</span><span style='color:black'>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_314731887\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2023\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_314731887\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Persoanele care exercit&#259; dreptul prev&#259;zut la\nalin. (1) trebuie s&#259; fi avut deja calitatea de <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionar</span>\nla data la care a fost dezb&#259;tut&#259; în cadrul adun&#259;rii generale\nproblema introducerii <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iunii</span> în\nr&#259;spundere.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1934000243\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2022\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1934000243\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)Cheltuielile de judecat&#259; vor fi suportate de <span\nclass=SpellE>ac&#355;ionarii</span> care au introdus <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iunea</span>.\nÎn caz de admitere, <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionarii</span> au dreptul la\nrambursarea de c&#259;tre societate a sumelor avansate cu acest titlu.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1246378473\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2021\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1246378473\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)Dup&#259; r&#259;mânerea definitiv&#259; a\nhot&#259;rârii <span class=SpellE>instan&#355;ei</span> de admitere a <span\nclass=SpellE>ac&#355;iunii</span> prev&#259;zute la alin. (1), adunarea\ngeneral&#259; a <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionarilor</span>, respectiv\nconsiliul de supraveghere va putea decide încetarea mandatului\nadministratorilor, directorilor <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> membrilor\nconsiliului de supraveghere, respectiv al membrilor directoratului, <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> înlocuirea acestora.</span><br style='mso-special-character:\nline-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}